title: Hour 1 - MLB Playoff Excitement, Vols Upset 'Bama
itunes:title: Hour 1 - MLB Playoff Excitement, Vols Upset 'Bama
description:
Ross Tucker is filling in for Dan Patrick and he has enjoyed the MLB Playoffs very much to date. Plus he discusses the repercussions of Tennessee upsetting Alabama and how it will affect the landscape of college football.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
